    "description": "Aman Resorts India Advisory Limited is actively seeking a talented and motivated Revenue Manager to join our dynamic team in Ludhiana. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Aman Resorts India Advisory Limited:\nAman Resorts India Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in Crisis Management\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Professional development and training programs\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ludhiana, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Aman Resorts India Advisory Limited!",
